      "rationale": "Validation QOI (principal surface strain at gauge locations) is directly related to the COU QOI (peak von Mises stress in the stem). Strain and stress are linked through the constitutive law; surface strains are a sensitive indicator of sub-surface stress concentrations. Mapping between validation QOI and COU QOI documented in model credibility plan MCP-2024-THA-001."
