      "rationale": "Simulation execution checklist completed by primary analyst and independently reviewed by a second qualified engineer. Model inputs verified against source data prior to each simulation run. Boundary condition application reviewed against loading protocol. No discrepancies identified during independent review. Use error controls documented in SOP-FEA-2024-007."
