      "rationale": "Linear elastic, isotropic material model adopted for cortical bone after comparative study against transversely isotropic formulation. Isotropic model error relative to strain gauge data (6.8%) is within acceptance threshold and is conservative for peak stress prediction. Geometric nonlinearity assessed via eigenvalue analysis; linear geometry confirmed adequate (displacement/thickness < 0.05). Model form uncertainty quantified by comparing isotropic and transversely isotropic predictions; difference < 10% at all gauge locations."
